extendedData.value:
Your first step into the ever-changing world of Magic: The Gathering. Portal makes it easy to master the many facets of the world's original trading card game!
OBJECT OF THE GAME
You and your opponent are rival wizards dueling for control of a magical plane. Reduce your opponent's score from 20 to 0 before he or she does the same to you!

Contents:
The Official Guide to Portal
Two 35-card preconstructed decks
Two 15-card booster packs
Two score-keeping beads
Two playmats, which show players where to place their cards
Step-by-step play guide, illustrating five turns of a sample game
Rulebook
